隨著 EA 加拿大與[[EA_Black_Box|Black Box]]2012年的整併並定位專注於線上免費遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/334628/ea-confirms-vancouver-studio-layoffs/|title=EA confirms Vancouver studio layoffs|last=Robinson|first=Andy|publisher=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]|date=2012-02-06|accessdate=2013-01-26|archive-date=2014-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214204336/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/334628/ea-confirms-vancouver-studio-layoffs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，EA提前於2011年建立起新的工作室—— EA 歌德堡（現Ghost Games）。EA歌德堡位於[[瑞典|瑞典]][[哥德堡|哥德堡]]，專門負責開發[[寒霜引擎|寒霜引擎]]遊戲<ref>{{cite web |title=What We Do – EA Gothenburg |url=http://eagothenburg.ea.com/what-we-do/ |publisher=[[EA_Gothenburg|EA Gothenburg]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6C5fFAsdY?url=http://eagothenburg.ea.com/what-we-do/ |archivedate=2012-11-11 |accessdate=2012-11-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/03/05/ea-gothenburg-studio-to-focus-on-frostbite-development/ |title=EA Gothenburg studio to focus on Frostbite development |publisher=VG247 |date=2012-03-05 |accessdate=2012-11-17 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804033058/https://www.vg247.com/2012/03/05/ea-gothenburg-studio-to-focus-on-frostbite-development/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=EA Gothenburg hiring for new Need for Speed |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/372103/ea-gothenburg-hiring-for-new-need-for-speed |publisher=CVG |accessdate=2012-11-15 |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211104049/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/372103/ea-gothenburg-hiring-for-new-need-for-speed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、當中包括極速快感系列的開發工作<ref name=NewNFSconfirmed>{{cite web |url=http://www.videogamer.com/xbox360/need_for_speed_most_wanted_2012/news/confirmed_ea_gothenburg_developing_unannounced_need_for_speed.html |title=Confirmed: EA Gothenburg developing unannounced Need For Speed |publisher=Videogamer.com |